  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057060/extras/f75c22be4862dc0ee2f330871d7d2af7.poster.avif?t=1725465567\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057060/extras/f75c22be4862dc0ee2f330871d7d2af7.webm?t=1725465567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057060/extras/f75c22be4862dc0ee2f330871d7d2af7.mp4?t=1725465567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>ARCADE SOCCER WITH MINIMAL RULES AND MAXIMUM POWERS</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Online Multiplayer</strong></h2>Join or create a lobby and play with up to 7 other players for a chaotic and fun soccer experience.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Single Player Mode</strong></h2>Choose a team and challenge AI opponents.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Character Editor</strong></h2>Customize your character's appearance and abilities.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Realistic Ball Physics</strong></h2>Experience authentic ball movement.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057060/extras/ad60d6ee57b72c32729a35cad06c4fb0.poster.avif?t=1725465567\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057060/extras/ad60d6ee57b72c32729a35cad06c4fb0.webm?t=1725465567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057060/extras/ad60d6ee57b72c32729a35cad06c4fb0.mp4?t=1725465567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- No Red Cards, No Yellow Cards</strong></h2>It's all about the fun!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057060/extras/5b43d00df1ec1b695c93be3712dcc8d9.poster.avif?t=1725465567\" width=600 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057060/extras/5b43d00df1ec1b695c93be3712dcc8d9.webm?t=1725465567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057060/extras/5b43d00df1ec1b695c93be3712dcc8d9.mp4?t=1725465567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057060/extras/f75c22be4862dc0ee2f330871d7d2af7.poster.avif?t=1725465567\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057060/extras/f75c22be4862dc0ee2f330871d7d2af7.webm?t=1725465567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057060/extras/f75c22be4862dc0ee2f330871d7d2af7.mp4?t=1725465567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>ARCADE SOCCER WITH MINIMAL RULES AND MAXIMUM POWERS</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Online Multiplayer</strong></h2>Join or create a lobby and play with up to 7 other players for a chaotic and fun soccer experience.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Single Player Mode</strong></h2>Choose a team and challenge AI opponents.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Character Editor</strong></h2>Customize your character's appearance and abilities.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Realistic Ball Physics</strong></h2>Experience authentic ball movement.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057060/extras/ad60d6ee57b72c32729a35cad06c4fb0.poster.avif?t=1725465567\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057060/extras/ad60d6ee57b72c32729a35cad06c4fb0.webm?t=1725465567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057060/extras/ad60d6ee57b72c32729a35cad06c4fb0.mp4?t=1725465567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- No Red Cards, No Yellow Cards</strong></h2>It's all about the fun!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057060/extras/5b43d00df1ec1b695c93be3712dcc8d9.poster.avif?t=1725465567\" width=600 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057060/extras/5b43d00df1ec1b695c93be3712dcc8d9.webm?t=1725465567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057060/extras/5b43d00df1ec1b695c93be3712dcc8d9.mp4?t=1725465567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
